e%20dark%2C%20either.%20Gyms%20have%20access%20to%20all%20of%20the%20data%20stored%20on%20their%20treadmills%20showing%20exactly%20how%20often%20people%20are%20using%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20go%20and%20use%20a%20code%20on%20an%20elliptical%20or%20I%20can%20use%20a%20code%20on%20a%20stair%20climber%20and%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20how%20many%20hours%20it's%20been%20used%20over%20the%20last%20month%2C%20three%20months%2C%20six%20months%2C%20whatever%20it%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20McCall%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGym%20managers%20can%20use%20that%20data%20to%20determine%20how%20they%20might%20want%20to%20remodel%20their%20space%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20do.%20%26quot%3BSome%20health%20clubs%20are%20building%20new%20locations%20without%20cycling%20studios%2C%20I%20mean%2C%20that's%20how%20much%20that%20group%20fitness%20is%20being%20affected%2C%26quot%3B%20McCall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20new%20demand%20for%20specialized%20muscle%20gyms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22man%20with%20barbell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e48108cfb7f307e57180c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMoMo%20Productions%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGym-goers%20are%20increasingly%20seeking%20out%20more%20specialized%20spaces%2C%20and%20not%20just%20for%20spin%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20JDI%20Barbell%2C%20a%20strength-focused%20gym%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20opened%20in%202016%2C%20it%20was%20a%20small%20operation%2C%20popular%20with%20seasoned%20gym-goers%20looking%20to%20step%20up%20their%20game.%20It%20started%20out%20as%20one%20of%20a%20few%20exercise%20spaces%20dedicated%20to%20powerlifting%2C%20strongman%20exercises%2C%20and%20Olympic-style%20weightlifting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELately%2C%20business%20is%20booming%20even%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20reasons%20we%20get%20people%20coming%20in%3A%2050%25%20or%20more%20of%20members%20come%20to%20us%20after%20leaving%20a%20commercial%20gym%20because%20they're%20looking%20for%20something%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Priscilla%20Del%20Moral%2C%20JDI's%20co-owner%20and%20manager%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMiriam%20Fried%2C%20a%20New%20York%20City-based%20personal%20trainer%20and%20founder%20of%20MF%20Strong%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20she's%20seen%20the%20same%20trend%20at%20her%20gym%3A%20clients%20wanting%20more%20strength-focused%20workouts%20after%20tiring%20of%20the%20cardio-heavy%20fitness%20classes%20at%20bigger%20gyms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20helped%20fuel%20a%20resurgence%20of%20small%20gyms%2C%20which%20can%20focus%20on%20catering%20to%20a%20more%20individualized%20experience%20than%20their%20big-box%20counterparts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20have%20a%20million%20different%20types%20of%20machines%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20missing%20the%20'it'%20factor%20that%20makes%20people%20feel%20welcome%20and%20supported%2C%20they%20may%20not%20want%20to%20keep%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20Del%20Moral%2C%20who%20founded%20a%20nonprofit%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.strongurlsclub.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Strong%20Gurls%20Club%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20this%20the%20death%20of%20the%20elliptical%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20doesn't%20mean%20cardio%20is%20out.%20But%20it's%20being%20forced%20into%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20makeover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20now%20know%20that%20strength%20training%20is%20really%20good%20for%20you%20and%20that's%20here%20to%20stay%2C%20but%20we%20know%20you%20still%20need%20to%20go%20for%20walks%20and%20get%20your%20heart%20rate%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Natalia%20Mehlman%20Petrzela%2C%20professor%20of%20history%20at%20the%20New%20School%20and%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BFit%20Nation%3A%20The%20Gains%20and%20Pains%20of%20America's%20Exercise%20Obsession%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20treadmill%20is%20not%20disappearing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrands%20that%20manufacture%20cardio%20equipment%20are%20looking%20at%20tweaks%20they%20can%20make.%20StairMaster's%20parent%20company%2C%20Core%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Fitness%2C%20has%20been%20building%20out%20its%20fleet%20of%20machines%2C%20acquiring%20Jacob's%20Ladder%2C%20offering%20a%20new%20self-powered%20treadmill%2C%20and%20developing%20more%20assault-style%20bikes.%20They're%20branding%20themselves%20as%20more%20of%20a%20high-intensity%20training%20equipment%20provider%20than%20just%20a%20stair-climbing%20apparatus%20provider%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22assault%20bike%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e48191cfb7f307e5718104%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAssault-style%20bikes%20are%20great%20for%20high-intensity%20interval%20training.%3Cp%3EWestend61%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIncreasing%20enthusiasm%20for%20strength-training%20and%20longevity%20is%20also%20a%20boon%20for%20the%20fitness%20industry%20%E2%80%93%20potentially%20keeping%20people%20in%20the%20gym%20for%20way%20more%20years%20than%20they%20might%20have%20been%20capable%20of%20before.%20Strength%20training%20is%20ideal%20for%20extending%20your%20%26quot%3Bplay%20span%2C%26quot%3B%20your%20ability%20to%20keep%20doing%20what%20you%20love%20as%20you%20age.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaietta%2C%20the%20Crunch%20manager%20in%20New%20York%2C%20said%20he%20(41)%20is%20still%20showing%20up%20athletes%20who%20are%20years%20younger%20than%20him.%20He%20credits%20that%20to%20his%20lifting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20strength%20training%20really%20affords%20people%20is%20to%20make%20age%20just%20feel%20like%20a%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20artic