20built%20out%20of%20spite%20%E2%80%94%20from%20a%20feud%20between%20two%20brothers%20%E2%80%94%20has%20made%20the%20property%20a%20viral%20phenomenon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20story%20about%20the%20skinny%20house's%20spiteful%20origins%20may%20not%20be%20true.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOne%20oft-repeated%20story%20says%20the%20skinny%20house%20was%20built%20out%20of%20spite%20by%20an%20angry%20brother%20in%20the%201800s.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20of%20a%20plaque%20hanging%20in%20the%20front%20of%20Boston's%20skinny%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66db59985444ffafa7636784%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20sign%20that%20says%20the%20home%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bspite%20house%26quot%3B%20hangs%20from%20the%20front%20facade.%3Cp%3ECL%20Properties%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%202015%20Boston%20magazine%20roundup%20of%20all%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bspite%20houses%26quot%3B%20in%20New%20England%20nicely%20summarized%20the%20most%20popular%20legend%20surrounding%2044%20Hull%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20on%20which%20the%20skinny%20house%20now%20sits%20was%20inherited%20by%20two%20brothers%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20served%20in%20the%20Civil%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20brother%20returned%20from%20war%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20his%20sibling%20had%20spent%20the%20time%20building%20a%20large%20house%20on%20most%20of%20the%20plot%20of%20land%20they%20were%20supposedly%20going%20to%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20revenge%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0or%20spite%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20brother%20who'd%20served%20in%20the%20war%20decided%20to%20build%20himself%20a%20skinny%20house%20around%201862%20to%20block%20the%20sunlight%20that%20his%20brother's%20property%20would%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20slightly%20different%20version%20of%20that%20origin%20story%20dates%20back%20to%20a%201920%20newspaper%20article.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221528%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20clip%20of%20an%20article%20published%20in%20the%20Boston%20Globe%20in%201920.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66db5261a0ff598b26657dfc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222013%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%201920%2C%20the%20Boston%20Globe%20published%20an%20article%20with%20a%20version%20of%20the%20skinny%20house's%20origin%20story.%3Cp%3EThe%20Boston%20Globe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201920%2C%20the%20Boston%20Globe%20published%20one%20of%20the%20earliest%20articles%20referencing%20a%20%26quot%3Bspite%26quot%3B%20myth%20associated%20with%2044%20Hull%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20author%2C%20however%2C%20recounts%20a%20slightly%20different%20perception.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20describes%20a%20tale%20that%20says%20the%20house%20was%20erected%20during%20a%20land%20dispute%20between%20warring%20neighbors%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0one%20of%20whom%20was%20supposedly%20a%20%26quot%3BTory%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20someone%20who%20supported%20Great%20Britain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20article%2C%20though%2C%20doubt%20is%20cast%20on%20the%20notion%20the%20house%20was%20built%20out%20of%20spite.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20refers%20to%20a%20map%20held%20by%20the%20Bostonian%20Society%20that%20showed%20the%20house%20was%20not%20built%20until%20after%201874%2C%20%26quot%3Bgiving%20the%20lie%20to%20the%20old%20legend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20land%20was%20empty%20until%20multiple%20properties%20were%20built%20there%20in%20the%20late%201800s%2C%20old%20maps%20show.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20staircase%20and%20living%20area%20in%20a%20tiny%20home%20in%20Boston.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66df5dd95444ffafa763d763%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22854%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20house%20sold%20to%20its