20encouraged%20her%20to%20pick%20up%20an%20old%20hobby%3A%20sneaker%20collecting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20like%2C%20'You%20always%20talk%20about%20how%20much%20you%20love%20sneakers%20and%20reminisce%20about%20this%20thing%20you%20did%20with%20your%20dad.%20What%20if%20you%20do%20it%20as%20a%20hobby%20to%20decompress%20a%20little%20bit%3F'%26quot%3B%20recalled%20Zapata%2C%20who%20used%20to%20wait%20outside%20Foot%20Locker%20with%20her%20dad%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%20on%20big%20sneaker%20release%20days.%20%26quot%3BMy%20dad%20would%20do%20anything%20with%20me%20when%20I%20was%20little.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%20dad%20couldn't%20always%20afford%20to%20buy%20her%20a%20new%20pair%20of%20Nikes%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20when%20we%20wanted%20something%2C%20he%20would%20do%20anything%20to%20figure%20it%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20That's%20how%20the%20sneaker-flipping%20hobby%20came%20about.%20%26quot%3BHe%20would%20be%20like%2C%20'OK%2C%20you%20want%20one%20of%20these%20sneakers%3F%20Let's%20buy%20five%20of%20them%2C%20sell%20them%2C%20collect%20that%20%2430%20or%20%2440%20or%20%2450%20profit%2C%20and%20then%20we'll%20buy%20you%20your%20pair.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20car%20dealer%2C%20%26quot%3Bhe%20loved%20buying%20and%20reselling%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20Turns%20out%2C%20it%20ran%20in%20the%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224a8abb8e-38cb-43e9-b120-4fc74b06eaee%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EReconnecting%20with%20sneaker-flipping%20during%20Covid%20%E2%80%94%20and%20turning%20the%20hobby%20into%20a%20side%20hustle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20early%20pandemic%20was%20an%20ideal%20time%20for%20Zapata%20and%20her%20dad%20to%20settle%20into%20their%20old%20routine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20both%20stuck%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20started%20d