ns%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpotify%20just%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20it's%20testing%20a%20new%20parental%20control%20feature%20that%20will%20allow%20parents%20to%20block%20explicit%20lyrics%20and%20other%20content.%20As%20a%20parent%2C%20I%20say%20it%20took%20them%20long%20enough!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fspotify-family-plan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpotify%20has%20a%20stand-alone%20app%2C%20Spotify%20Kids%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20Kids%20app%20is%20really%20aimed%20at%20toddlers%20and%20preschoolers%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%26quot%3BBaby%20Shark%26quot%3B%20set.%20It%20has%20a%20really%20limited%20selection%20of%20songs%20(for%20example%2C%20a%20bunch%20of%20Taylor%20Swift%20songs%2C%20but%20almost%20nothing%20from%20her%20latest%20album).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20leaves%20a%20gap%20for%20older%20elementary%20school-age%20children%20who%20are%20starting%20to%20form%20their%20own%20musical%20tastes%2C%20but%20for%20whom%20the%20full%20library%20of%20modern%20music%20is%20not%20exactly%20appropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20pilot%20program%20will%20be%20for%20people%20who%20create%20a%20new%20kid%20account%20to%20be%20managed%20as%20part%20of%20a%20Family%20Account.%20For%20now%2C%20it%20is%20available%20only%20in%203%20countries%20(Denmark%2C%20Sweden%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand)%20but%20hopefully%20will%20roll%20out%20to%20more%20countries%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20all%20accounts%2C%20it's%20possible%2C%20deep%20within%20user%20settings%2C%20to%20turn%20off%20explicit%20lyrics%2C%20which%20makes%20songs%20marked%20%26quot%3BE%26quot%3B%20unplayable.%20However%2C%20this%20isn't%20a%20solution%20designed%20like%20a%20parental%20control%3A%20The%20user%20can%20easily%20turn%20this%20setting%20off.%20If%20you%20click%20on%20a%20song%20with%20explicit%20lyrics%2C%20you'll%20get%20a%20pop-up%20saying%20that%20it%20can't%20be%20played.%20It%20will%20direct%20you%20to%20the%20exact%20toggle%20switch%20in%20Settings%20to%20turn%20explicit%20content%20back%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20parental%20controls%20will%20allow%20a%20parent%20to%20set%20this%20up%20in%20a%20way%20that%20kids%20can't%20just%20turn%20it%20back%20off.%20They'll%20also%20offer%20the%20ability%20to%20block%20specific%20artists%20or%20songs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20feature%20allows%20parents%20to%20block%20or%20limit%20the%20videos%20on%20Spotify%20(including%20the%20short%20looping%20videos%20that%20play%20over%20a%20song).%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaked-deck-how-spotify-competing-for-video-ad-dollars-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpotify%20is%20pushing%20deeper%20and%20deeper%20into%20video%20podcasts%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20business%20strategy%2C%20this%20matters%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20second%20grader%20who%20really%20enjoyed%20being%20able%20to%20listen%20to%20music%20on%20Spotify%20%E2%80%94%20he%20set%20up%20a%20playlist%20with%20favorite%20songs%20he%20had%20heard%20on%20the%20radio%20and%20started%20to%20add%20other%20songs%20he%20discovered%20through%20Spotify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20eventually%2C%20I%20noticed%20that%20he%20was%20coming%20across%20other%20kinds%20of%20stuff.%20There%20were%20meme-y%20songs%20with%20Gen%20Alpha%20slang%20like%20%26quot%3BSigma%20playlist.%26quot%3B%20There%20was%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20video%20podcast%20content%20that%20basically%20looked%20like%20some%20YouTube%20content%2C%20like%20videos%20of%20people%20playing%20Minecraft%20or%20other%20video%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20parent%2C%20I'm%20not%20overly%20concerned%20with%20some%20bad%20words%20in%20popular%20songs.%20But%20Spotify%20isn't%20just%20for%20music%20anymore%2C%20and%20the%20amount%20of%20video%20content%20and%20other%20stuff%20made%20me%20realize%20that%20Spotify%20wasn't%20an%20app%20that%20%E2%80%94%20for%20now%20%E2%80%94%20I%20felt%20comfortable%20letting%20my%20kid%20use%20on%20his%20own.%20I%20deleted%20it%20from%20his%20iPad.%20Which%20stinks!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20this%20rolls%20out%20very%20soon%20in%20the%20US%20because%20no%20one%20will%20be%20more%20excited%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20back%20on%20Spotify%20than%20a%20certain%20member%20of%20my%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-parental-controls-kids-under-13-parents-how-to-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726304521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e498fcd17aa3c7b2b29b2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-parental-controls-kids-under-13-parents-how-to-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parental%20controls%20to%20block%20explicit%20lyrics%20and%20video%20content%20are%20finally%20coming%20to%20Spotify.%20But%20it%20might%20be%20a%20while%20before%20we%20can%20actually%20use%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-parental-controls-kids-under-13-parents-how-to-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22USS%20White%20River%3A%20How%20the%20US%20Navy%20transformed%20a%20landing%20vessel%20into%20a%20legendary%20rocket%20artillery%20ship%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20USS%20White%20River%20and%20its%20rockets%20supported%20troops%20fighting%20in%20Korea%20and%20Vietnam%20with%20fast%20and%20high-volume%20artillery%20support.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e1b1c383b8099cf9fd7db2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221379%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20USS%20White%20River%20and%20its%20rockets%20supported%20troops%20fighting%20in%20Korea%20and%20Vietnam