20the%20West%20Bengal%20health%20department%2C%20on%20Tuesday.%20There%20have%20been%20moves%20for%20a%20discussion%20between%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20doctors%20since%20then%20but%20they%20have%20been%20getting%20stalled%2C%20most%20recently%20over%20the%20protestors'%20demand%20for%20live%20streaming%20of%20the%20talks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20reached%20the%20protest%20site%20on%20Saturday%20and%20struck%20a%20conciliatory%20tone%2C%20asking%20if%20she%20could%20address%20the%20doctors.%20Amid%20slogan-shouting%20she%20said%20in%20Bengali%2C%20%26quot%3BPlease%20listen%20to%20me%20for%20five%20minutes%20and%20then%20shout%20slogans%2C%20it%20is%20your%20democratic%20right%20to%20do%20so.%20I%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Against%20the%20advice%20of%20my%20security%20officers%2C%20I%20have%20come%20here%20to%20salute%20your%20protests.%20I%20have%20also%20been%20part%20of%20student%20movements%2C%20I%20know%20my%20post%20is%20not%20a%20big%20deal%2C%20your%20voice%20is.%20It%20was%20raining%20all%20night%20and%20you%20suffered.%20I%20couldn't%20sleep%20either%20because%20I%20was%20feeling%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcknowledging%20that%20the%20protests%20had%20been%20going%20on%20for%20over%20a%20month%2C%20she%20urged%20the%20protesting%20doctors%20to%20return%20to%20work%2C%20assuring%20them%20that%20the%20government%20would%20lend%20a%20sympathetic%20ear%20to%20their%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20study%20the%20demands%2C%20I%20don't%20run%20the%20government%20alone.%20I%20will%20speak%20to%20the%20chief%20secretary%2C%20home%20secretary%20and%20director%20general%20of%20police.%20Action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20who%20are%20found%20guilty.%20I%20want%20justice%20for%20Tilottama%20(the%20name%20given%20to%20the%20woman%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered).%20From%20your%20platform%2C%20I%20will%20request%20the%20CBI%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20investigation.%20I%20request%20you%2C%20I%20need%20some%20time%20to%20consider%20your%20demands.%20If%20you%20trust%20me%2C%20come%20and%20talk%20to%20me%2C%20I%20will%20look%20into%20your%20demands%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20assured%20the%20doctors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrging%20the%20protesters%20to%20return%20to%20work%2C%20she%20said%20their%20families%20were%20worried%20about%20them%20and%20many%20patients%20had%20died%20because%20they%20did%20not%20get%20proper%20healthcare.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReturn%20to%20work.%20I%20will%20ensure%20that%20no%20injustice%20happens.%20I%20will%20set%20up%20committees%20in%20every%20hospital%20which%20will%20have%20senior%20and%20junior%20doctors%20as%20members.%20Everyone%20found%20guilty%20will%20be%20punished%2C%20it%20is%20not%20like%20they%20are%20my%20friends%20(referring%20to%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20resignation%20of%20some%20officials).%20Please%20talk%20amongst%20yourselves%20and%20return%20to%20work%2C%20I%20will%20not%20take%20any%20action.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20action%20was%20taken%2C%20I%20won't%20do%20that.%20I%20know%20you%20work%20a%20lot%2C%20I%20know%20how%20important%20you%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20last%20attempt%20to%20resolve%20the%20crisis...%20if%20you%20keep%20your%20faith%20in%20me%2C%20I%20will%20look%20into%20your%20complaints.%20The%20case%20is%20on%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20(which%20had%20set%20a%20September%2010%20deadline%20for%20the%20doctors%20to%20return%20to%20work)%20and%20the%20next%20hearing%20is%20on%20Tuesday.%20I%20don't%20want%20you%20to%20suffer.%20I%20have%20come%20to%20make%20a%20request%20as%20your%20%3Cem%3E'didi'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(big%20sister)%2C%20not%20as%20a%20chief%20minister.%20I%20am%20empathetic%20and%20I%20support%20your%20protest...%20I%20had%20also%20gone%20on%20a%20hunger%20strike%20for%2026%20days%20(during%20the%20protest%20against%20the%20acquisition%20of%20farmland%20in%20Singur)%2C%20but%20no%20one%20from%20the%20then%20government%20came%20to%20speak%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoctors'%20Take%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20shouted%20%26quot%3Bwe%20want%20justice%26quot%3B%20loudly%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20address%20and%2C%20talking%20to%20reporters%20after%20she%20finished%20speaking%2C%20some%20of%20the%20protesters%20said%20that%20while%20they%20welcomed%20her%20overture%2C%20they%20want%20a%20%26quot%3Btransparent%26quot%3B%20meeting%20-%20referring%20to%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20live%20telecast%20of%20discussions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20welcome%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20visit.%20We%20are%20ready%20to%20hold%20talks%20with%20her.%20Media%20is%20present%20here.%20Let%20there%20be%20a%20transparent%20meeting%20with%20her%20over%20our%20five%20demands%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20protesting%20doctor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBone%20Of%20Contention%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20government%20had%20invited%20the%20doctors%20for%20talks%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20but%20they%20had%20rejected%20the%20invite%20because%20it%20had%20come%20from%20the%20health%20secretary%2C%20whose%20resignation%20they%20are%20seeking.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20doctors%20had%20made%20four%20key%20demands%20for%20the%20discussion%20to%20take%20place%3A%20they%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20send%20a%20delegation%20of%20at%20least%2030%2C%20the%20discussion%20should%20be%20held%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20it%20should%20be%20centred%20around%20their%20five-point%20demands%2C%20and%20the%20meeting%20should%20be%20live%20telecast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20four%20demands%20for%20talks%20had%20been%20met%20and%20the%20doctors%20had%20reached%20the%20state%20secretariat%20on%20Thursday%20for%20a%20meeting%20but%20it%20did%20not%20take%20place%20because%20the%20government%20did%20not%20agree%20to%20its%20live%20streaming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20rationale%20after%20Thursday's%20meeting%20did%20not%20happen%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20said%20she%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20the%20doctors%20for%20over%20two%20hours%2C%20stated%20that%20the%20matter%20was%20in%20court%20and%20live%20streaming%20the%20meeting%20would%20be%20against%20protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20apologised%20to%20the%20people%20of%20West%20Bengal%20and%20said%20she%20was%20willing%20to%20step%20down%2C%20but%20also%20spoke%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20colour%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-point%20demands%20of%20the%20doctors%20include%20holding%20all%20individuals%20responsible%20for%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20-%20as%20well%20as%20any%20destruction%20of%20evidence%20-%20accountable%20and%20punishing%20them%20and%20taking%20strict%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20former%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20Principal%20Sandip%20Ghosh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20also%20pushed%20for%20the%20resignation%20of%20Kolkata%20Police%20Commissioner%20Vineet%20Goyal%20and%20Health%20Secretary%20Narayan%20Swaroop%20Nigam%2C%20among%20others%3B%20ensuring%20adequate%20security%20measures%20for%20healthcare%20workers%3B%20and%20eliminating%20a%20'threat%20culture'%20prevailing%20in%20government%20healthcare%20institutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726304100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Ffhcgo96_mamata-banerjee-at-doctors-protest-site-ndtv_625x300_14_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-arrives-at-protest-site-to-meet-doctors-agitating-over-rape-murder-6563221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taking%20a%20surprise%20step%20to%20end%20the%20impasse%20between%20her%20government%20and%20protesting%20doctors%