20the%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20rising%20home%20values%2C%20strong%20employment%20figures%2C%20a%20booming%20stock%20market%2C%20and%20cooling%20inflation%2C%20US%20household%20finances%20appear%20to%20be%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-americans-build-wealth-changing-stocks-homes-people-missed-out-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20remarkably%20good%20spot%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Americans%20are%20not%20a%20monolith%2C%20as%20Jefferies%20consumer%20strategist%20Carey%20Kaufman%20pointed%20out%20in%20a%20note%20to%20clients%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20U.S.%20consumer%20is%20three%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%3A%20the%20top%20fifth%20of%20the%20income%20scale%2C%20the%20bottom%20fifth%2C%20and%20the%20middle%20three-fifths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeading%20into%20the%20autumn%2C%20a%20considerable%20number%20of%20those%20in%20the%20bottom%20quintile%20appear%20to%20be%20running%20on%20borrowed%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22739846fc-9a1d-438a-b3ae-10a6df2e3f47%5C%22%3ETelling%20signs%20from%20spending%20at%20auto%20parts%20and%20dollar%20stores%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20the%20rosy%20outlook%20from%20stores%20that%20serve%20relatively%20large%20(and%20growing)%20shares%20of%20middle-%20and%20upper-income%20customers%2C%20auto%20parts%20and%20dollar%20store%20retailers%20are%20telling%20a%20more%20complicated%20story%20among%20their%20core%20customers%20who%20have%20lower%20household%20incomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20times%20are%20good%2C%20our%20core%20customer%20normally%20works%20her%2030-%20to%2040-hour%20a%20week%20job%2C%20but%20also%20has%20a%20secondary%20job%20that%20she%20normally%20works%2015%20to%2025%20hours%20in.%20What%20she%20told%20us%20in%20Q2%20was%20that%20is%20going%20away%20or%20has%20gone%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Dollar%20General%20CEO%20Ted%20Vasos%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20at%20the%20Goldman%20Sachs%20Global%20Retailing%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVasos%20said%20that%20reduction%20in%20earnings%2C%20coupled%20with%20higher%20prices%20from%20years%20of%20inflation%2C%20has%20put%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdollar-general-shows-how-bad-economy-is-for-some-shoppers-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreased%20pressure%20on%20lower-income%20households%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20things%20continue%20according%20to%20historical%20trends%2C%20those%20concerns%20begin%20to%20get%20more%20serious%20for%20middle%20and%20upper-income%20segments%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20things%20start%20to%20move%20south%20in%20the%20economy%2C%20our%20core%20customer%20feels%20it%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Vasos%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20usually%20see%20it%20before%20most%20retailers%20start%20to%20feel%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDollar%20Tree%2C%20which%20owns%20Family%20Dollar%2C%20reported%20similar%20consumer%20headwinds%20during%20its%20quarterly%20earnings%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuto%20parts%20stores%20are%20another%20retail%20category%20that%20is%20especially%20tuned%20in%20to%20what's%20happening%20at%20the%20lower%20ends%20of%20the%20economic%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20their%20consumer-facing%20business%20is%20driven%20by%20helping%20people%20keep%20their%20cars%20and%20trucks%20running%20smoothly%2C%20Mizuho%20analyst%20David%20Bellinger%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20lower%20end%20consumer%20who%20works%20on%20their%20car%20out%20of%20economic%20necessity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20maybe%20if%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20make%20a%20fix%2C%20they%20could%20delay%20a%20few%20months.%20That's%20kind%20of%20what's%20happening%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvance%20Auto%20Parts%20CFO%20Ryan%20Grimsland%20said%20during%20the%20company's%20earnings%20call%20last%20month%20that%20DIY%20customers%20are%20deferring%20%26quot%3Bmaintenance%20that%20you%20would%20typically%20want%20to%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20skipping%20an%20oil%20change%20or%20ignoring%20a%20check-engine%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20can%20help%20extend%20the%20household%20budget%20for%20a%20time%2C%20but%20as%20Genuine%20Parts%20CEO%20Will%20Stengel%20put%20it%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20only%20so%20long%20you%20can%20defer%20an%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20repairs%20aren't%20the%20only%20auto-related%20expense%20seeing%20cut-backs.%20Ally%20Financial%20this%20week%20reported%20worse%20than%20expected%20loan%20performance%20in%20July%20and%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20borrower%20is%20struggling%20with%20high%20inflation%20and%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20and%20now%20more%20recently%2C%20a%20weakening%20employment%20picture%2C%26quot%3B%20Ally%20CFO%20Russell%20Hutchinson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Ffinance%2Fally-financial-flags-intensifying-credit-challenges-shares-slump-2024-09-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20deferred%20maintenance%20and%20missed%20payments%20have%20in%20common%20is%20they%20are%20both%20problems%20that%20get%20more%20expensive%20with%20time.%20Nobody%20wants%20to%20be%20stranded%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road%20or%20hounded%20by%20collections%20agents%2C%20but%20more%20people%20are%20finding%20themselves%20hoping%20to%20make%20it%20one%20day%20or%20week%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20as%20Dollar%20General's%20Vasos%20observed%2C%20paychecks%20aren't%20going%20as%20far%20as%20they%20once%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20noticed%20was%20an%20even%20tighter%20core%20consumer%20at%20the%20very%20last%20week%20of%20each%20of%20the%20months%20in%20Q2%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20that's%20always%20a%20tighter%20week%20of%20the%20month%20for%20our%20core%20consumer%2C%20it%20was%20by%20far%20the%20weakest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C