adlock%20With%20Doctors%2C%20Trinamool%20Leader's%20Big%20'Attack%20Conspiracy'%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20deadlock%20between%20protesting%20doctors%20and%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%2C%20senior%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20has%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3Bopposition%20forces%26quot%3B%20are%20plotting%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20agitators%20to%20defame%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20in%20the%20state.%20Mr%20Ghosh%20cited%20an%20audio%20clip%20of%20a%20conversation%20as%20proof%20of%20the%20conspiracy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20have%20been%20protesting%20since%20a%20trainee%20doctor%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20August%209.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20conversation%20is%20between%20a%20member%20of%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20Left%20and%20one%20from%20an%20ultra-Left%20organisation.%20There%20is%20a%20deep%20conspiracy%20against%20the%20government.%20They%20were%20talking%20about%20a%20plot.%20They%20will%20attack%20the%20%3Cem%3E'dharna'%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sit-in)%20of%20doctors%20and%20then%20will%20blame%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20the%20state%20government%20that%20after%20yesterday's%20deadlock%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20attacking%20the%20doctors...%20this%20is%20the%20main%20plot%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ghosh%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20made%20the%20same%20claim%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20and%20said%20the%20police%20should%20stop%20the%20entry%20of%20outsiders%20near%20the%20protest%20site%20at%20Swasthya%20Bhavan%2C%20the%20headquarters%20of%20the%20health%20department%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20in%20Kolkata's%20Salt%20Lake%2C%20where%20the%20doctors%20began%20a%20sit-in%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20on%20their%20own%20and%20also%20arrested%20one%20person.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECPI(M)%20spokesperson%20Fuad%20Halim%20said%20the%20police%20should%20investigate%20how%20Mr%20Ghosh%20got%20the%20clip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20August%2014%2C%20when%20a%20peaceful%20protest%20was%20on%2C%20a%20big%20group%20of%20goons%20entered%20RG%20Kar%20hospital%20and%20tried%20to%20compromise%20the%20scene%20of%20crime.%20The%20administration%20is%20totally%20silent%20on%20the%2020-30%20people%20who%20have%20been%20arrested%20-%20who%20they%20were%2C%20what%20are%20their%20political%20affiliations%2C%20why%20they%20went%20on%20a%20rampage.%20Devious%20forces%20are%20working%20here%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20is%20involved%20in%20a%20heinous%20threat%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Halim%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20moves%20for%20a%20discussion%20between%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20protesting%20doctors%20since%20Tuesday%2C%20which%20have%20been%20getting%20stalled.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20doctors%20had%20made%20four%20key%20demands%20for%20the%20discussion%20to%20take%20place%3A%20they%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20send%20a%20delegation%20of%20at%20least%2030%2C%20the%20discussion%20should%20be%20held%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20it%20should%20be%20centred%20around%20their%20five-point%20demands%2C%20and%20the%20meeting%20should%20be%20live%20telecast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20four%20demands%20had%20been%20met%20and%20the%20doctors%20had%20reached%20the%20state%20secretariat%20on%20Thursday%20for%20a%20meeting%20but%20it%20did%20not%20take%20place%20because%20the%20government%20did%20not%20agree%20to%20a%20'live%20telecast'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Against%20Protocol'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20reasoning%20after%20Thursday's%20meeting%20did%20not%20happen%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20said%20she%20had%20been%20waiting%20for%20the%20doctors%2