%2FFirst-sewage-treatment-plant-ladakh-1726237474-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFirst-sewage-treatment-plant-ladakh-1726237474-150x112.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366000%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22599%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E3%20MLD%20sewage%20treatment%20plant%20in%20Leh.%20(Images%20courtesy%20X%2Fsahilinfra2)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Dr%20Chorol%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20further%20consideration%2C%20I%20believe%20a%20decentralised%20approach%20might%20be%20more%20suitable%20and%20practical%20for%20Leh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%2C%20this%20includes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Small-scale%20treatment%20systems%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20could%20implement%20multiple%20smaller%20treatment%20facilities%20strategically%20located%20throughout%20Leh.%20These%20could%20serve%20clusters%20of%20households%20or%20neighbourhoods%2C%20reducing%20the%20need%20for%20extensive%20piping%20across%20difficult%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Advanced%20septic%20systems%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Promoting%20the%20use%20of%20modern%2C%20environmentally-friendly%20septic%20systems%20for%20individual%20households%20or%20small%20groups%20of%20homes%20could%20be%20effective.%20These%20systems%20can%20treat%20wastewater%20to%20a%20higher%20standard%20than%20traditional%20septic%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Constructed%20wetlands%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Where%20space%20allows%2C%20we%20could%20create%20artificial%20wetlands%20designed%20to%20naturally%20filter%20and%20treat%20wastewater.%20This%20eco-friendly%20approach%20could%20work%20well%20in%20some%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Dry%20toilets%20and%20composting%20systems%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGiven%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20water%20scarcity%2C%20expanding%20the%20u