nglish%20couple's%20country%20home%2C%20the%20Daltons%20(and%20particularly%20Ben)%20are%20eager%20to%20use%20it%20as%20an%20escape%20to%20reinvigorate%20their%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20quickly%20go%20downhill%20when%20it%20becomes%20clear%20that%20Paddy%20and%20Ciara's%20interest%20in%20the%20Daltons%20(and%20their%20own%20relationship%20with%20their%20son%2C%20Ant)%20is%20far%20more%20sinister%20than%20it%20initially%20appears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20new%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%20ahead%20of%20the%20film's%20release%20on%20Friday%2C%20McNairy%20discusses%20how%20he%20came%20aboard%20the%20project%2C%20which%20is%20a%20remake%20of%20the%202022%20Danish%20film%20%26quot%3BG%C3%A6sterne%26quot%3B%20(literally%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Guests%26quot%3B%20but%20marketed%20in%20its%20Sundance%20Film%20Festival%20premiere%20as%20%26quot%3BSpeak%20No%20Evil%26quot%3B)%2C%20and%20what%20he%20thought%20of%20the%20original.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a9ec188-bfa4-4c6c-8edf-d19c9f146001%5C%22%3EHow%20McNairy%20joined%20the%20'Speak%20No%20Evil'%20remake%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227339%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alix%20West%20Lefler%2C%20Scoot%20McNairy%2C%20and%20Mackenzie%20Davis%20in%20%26quot%3BSpeak%20No%20Evil%26quot%3B%20(2024)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e4ab67d17aa3c7b2b2a39c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlix%20West%20Lefler%2C%20Scoot%20McNairy%2C%20and%20Mackenzie%20Davis%20in%20%26quot%3BSpeak%20No%20Evil%26quot%3B%20(2024).%3Cp%3ESusie%20Allnutt%2FUniversal%20Pictures%20and%20Blumhouse%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMcNairy%2C%20an%20acclaimed%20character%20actor%20known%20for%20past%20roles%20in%20%26quot%3BKilling%20Them%20Softly%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BArgo%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20AMC%20series%20%26quot%3BHalt%20and%20Catch%20Fire%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20intrigued%20by%20the%20project%20when%20he%20found%20out%20that%20filmmaker%20James%20Watkins%20was%20at%20the%20helm%20and%20McAvoy%20was%20attached%20to%20star.%20He%20was%20excited%20to%20collaborate%20with%20them%20both%2C%20and%20that%20prompted%20his%20interest%20in%20checking%20out%20the%20original%20movie%2C%20which%20BI%20reporter%20Eammon%20Jacobs%20previously%20named%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-new-horror-movies-where-to-watch-pearl-deadstream-nanny-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20new%20horror%20movies%20of%202022%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20watched%20the%20original%20before%20I%20even%20read%20the%20James%20Watkins%20script%2C%26quot%3B%20McNairy%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20said%20he%20loved%20the%20original.%20In%20particular%2C%20he%20appreciated%20its%20tone%20and%20the%20simplicity%20of%20its%20plot%20(noteworthy%20for%20its%20nihilistic%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-front-room-ending-explained-brandy-horror-movie-eggers-brothers-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisturbing%20ending%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20thrilling%20as%20the%20prospect%20of%20working%20with%20Watkins%20and%20McAvoy%20was%2C%20%26quot%3Bwatching%20the%20original%20is%20what%20got%20me%20really%20excited%20about%20being%20involved%20in%20this%20franchise%2C%26quot%3B%20McNairy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227aad14f4-5f42-4320-81c4-8b77ae4e0c8f%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20'Speak%20No%20Evil'%20remake%20came%20about%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20did%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevery-disney-live-action-remake-ranked-from-worst-to-best-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremake%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20released%20only%20two%20years%20after%20the%20original%2C%20come%20to%20pass%20in%20the%20first%20place%3F%20It%20all%20started%20with%20Blumhouse%2C%20the%20production%20company%20behind%20the%20new%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20production%20notes%2C%20producer%20Jason%20Blum%20got%20a%20call%20from%20an%20executive%20at%20Universal%20Studios%20who'd%20seen%20the%20Danish%20movie%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-sundance-movies-where-to-watch-them-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20Sundance%20Film%20Festival%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20disturbed%20by%20it.%20Blum%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bfloored%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20saw%20the%20movie%2C%20and%20put%20it%20in%20Watkins'%20hands%2C%20already%20familiar%20with%20Watkins'%20work%20on%20%26quot%3BEden%20Lake%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Woman%20in%20Black.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Watkins%20took%20the%20crux%20and%20themes%20of%20the%20Danish%20movie%2C%20equal%20parts%20social%20satire%20and%20thriller%2C%20his%20film%20is%20a%20significant%20departure%20from%20the%20original.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20changes%20key%20details%20in%20the%20lead%20characters'%20identities%20(making%20the%20Daltons%20Americans%2C%20while%20Paddy%20and%20Ciara%20are%20country%20Brits)%2C%20and%20retools%20the%20entire%20third%20act%20to%20propel%20the%20audience%20to%20a%20new%20conclusion%20that's%20shocking%20in%20a%20different%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20is%20a%20worthy%20remake%2C%20grounded%20by%20McAvoy's%20deliciously%20unhinged%20performance%20as%20Paddy%20and%20McNairy's%20pitch-perfect%20haplessness%20as%20Ben%2C%20that%20tells%20a%20similar%20story%20with%20a%20slightly%20different%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BSpeak%20No%20Evil%26quot%3B%20is%20in%20theaters%20now.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspeak-no-evil-remake-vs-original-scoot-mcnairy-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726265724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e4a1d7d17aa3c7b2b2a082%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2