sing%20significant%20alterations%20to%20this%20delicate%20balance%2C%20leading%20to%20severe%20consequences%20for%20our%20groundwater%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-1726234110.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Overview%20of%20Leh%20Town%3A%20Climate%20change%20is%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20the%20region's%20groundwater%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-1726234110.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-1726234110-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-1726234110-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-1726234110-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FLeh-Town-1726234110-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365898%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOverview%20of%20Leh%20Town%3A%20Climate%20change%20is%20wreaking%20havoc%20on%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20groundwater%20(Image%20courtesy%20Wikimedia%20Commons)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%20is%20the%20increase%20in%20global%20temperatures.%20The%20rapid%20melting%20of%20glaciers%20leads%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20water%20flow%20during%20the%20summer%20months%2C%20but%20it%20also%20means%20that%20there%20is%20less%20water%20stored%20in%20the%20form%20of%20ice%20to%20sustain%20the%20flow%20during%20dry%20seasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20climate%20change%20is%20also%20altering%20precipitation%20patterns%20in%20Leh.%20We%20are%20experiencing%20more%20frequent%20and%20intense%20extreme%20weather%20events%2C%20such%20as%20heavy%20rainfall%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F323311%2Fhimachal-pradesh-floods-landslides-north-india-heavy-rains-kullu-kangra-mandi-emergency-helpline%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflash%20floods%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20these%20events%20do%20contribute%20to%20the%20recharge%20of%20our%20aquifers%20to%20some%20extent%2C%20they%20also%20lead%20to%20increased%20surface%20runoff%20and%20soil%20erosion.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20rainwater%20is%20lost%20before%20it%20can%20percolate%20into%20the%20ground%20and%20replenish%20our%20aquifers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Chorol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20factor%20to%20consider%20is%20the%20changing%20vegetation%20cover%20in%20the%20region.%20As%20temperatures%20rise%20and%20precipitation%20patterns%20change%2C%20we%20are%20observing%20shifts%20in%20the%20local%20ecosystem.%20Some%20native%20plant%20species%20like%20seabuckthorn%2C%20willow%20and%20poplar%20that%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20retaining%20moisture%20and%20promoting%20groundwater%20recharge%20are%20struggling%20to%20adapt%20to%20these%20new%20conditions.%20The%20loss%20of%20these%20species%20can%20further%20exacerbate%20the%20problem%20of%20reduced%20aquifer%20recharge%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBroken%20sewage%20system%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20state%20of%20Leh%E2%80%99s%20sewage%20system%20is%20a%20significant%20concern%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20groundwater.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20town%20lacks%20a%20comprehensive%20and%20efficient%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302015%2Fboson-whitewater-bengaluru-startup-converts-stp-water-to-high-quality-potable-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20targ