ammed%20C%20and%20Irfan%20Safar%20S%20started%20Fulva%20to%20retail%20authentic%20Kerala%20specialities%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20idolises%20the%20red%20variant%20(also%20the%20most%20popular%20flavour)%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eenjoys%20a%20gamut%20of%20flavour%20quotients.%20And%20understandably%2C%20Shaheem%20considers%20himself%20lucky%20to%20have%20lived%20and%20grown%20up%20in%20a%20city%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20mass-manufactured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20as%20fortunate.%20So%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20divulge%20an%20important%20piece%20of%20information.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20limited%20to%20Kozhikode%20anymore%20to%20get%20your%20fill%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Not%20just%20one%2C%20but%20an%20eclectic%20mix%20of%2024%20varieties%20will%20find%20their%20way%20to%20your%20doorstep%20if%20you%20wish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20brainwave%20by%20four%20childhood%20friends%20is%20making%20this%20possible.%20Their%20startup%20Fulva%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Kerala-based%20brand%20serving%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F286270%2Fmom-sells-authentic-maharashtrian-food-in-mumbai-pune-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eauthentic%20traditional%20food%20products%20%3C%2Fa%3Esourced%20from%20small-scale%20producers%20%E2%80%94%20is%20completing%20a%20year%20of%20operations%20and%20has%20already%20touched%20a%20milestone%20with%20a%20Rs%2084%20lakh%20turnover.%20And%20as%20they%20share%2C%20their%20success%20story%20is%20written%20by%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESquare-shaped%20pieces%20of%20history%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20visited%20Kozhikode%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20know%20it%20is%20almost%20a%20sacrilege%20to%20not%20return%20home%20with%20servings%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalw