lwas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20every%20kind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20friends%20fortified%20the%20idea%20of%20Fulva%2C%20they%20say%20nostalgia%20was%20a%20main%20ingredient.%20Thesreef%20pitches%20in%20here%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20if%20anyone%20in%20my%20family%20was%20going%20abroad%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20they%20always%20bought%20to%20take%20along%20was%20the%20Kozhikoden%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%20grew%20up%20with%20it%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337104%2Feasy-recipe-for-gajar-ka-halwa-history-winter-dessert%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20flavours%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ehave%20always%20made%20us%20huge%20fans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Irfan%20interjects%20here%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehalwa%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebeing%20in%20the%20market%20for%20the%20last%20500%20years%2C%20there%20is%20still%20no%20established%20brand%20for%20it%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20with%20many%20traditional%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20four%20friends%20at%20a%20Fulva%20pop-up%20store.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fkozhikoden-halwa-3-1725528932-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%